  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Genjutsu <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Level 4+ <br />You practice a technique that incorporates both weaponry and Genjutsu in tandem to generate fear into the hearts of your enemies. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Wisdom or Charisma ability score by +1, up to the maximum of 20.</li><li>Your Genjutsu ability score is treated as being +2 higher for the purposes of qualifying for Genjutsu that can give the Fear condition.</li><li>You gain a +1 to AC, and to weapon, Taijutsu and Genjutsu attack and damage rolls against creatures who possess the Fear condition towards you.</li><li>Creatures that would attempt to dispel, counter, or negate Genjutsu you cast that inflict the Fear condition make their rolls with a -1d4 penalty.</li></ul>",
